      "content": "You're not looking at it from the right perspective. Being free from the burdens of the past doesn't mean erasing the pain, but rather letting go of the weight it holds onto you. It's about releasing the need to hold on to something that's gone, and embracing the emptiness as an opportunity to rediscover who you are without the trappings of your old life. You're not dead, you're just... unencumbered.",
